(7081, 'Lamisil 1% topical cream 15 gm', 'لاميزيل 1% كريم 15 جرام', '', '16', 'Terbinafine', 'Novartis > glaxo smithkline', 'Cream', 'كريم', '', 'Antifungals.allylamines', '1%', 'Terbinafine hydrochloride is indicated to treat fungal skin and nail infections caused by _Trichophyton_ species, _Microsporum canis_, _Epidermophyton floccosum_,[L9068] and _Tinea_ species.[L9065] Terbinafine hydrochloride also treats yeast infections of the skin caused by _Candida_ species and _Malassezia furfur_.[L9068]', '6223002641062', '', 3695, '2022-12-06', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
