(33495, 'Relat hair lotion 120 ml', 'ريلات هير لوشن 120 مل', '195', '250', 'Caffeine 2% + vital hair & scalp complex + ginseng extract + garlic oil + panthenol + rosemary oil + marula oil + birch ext + peppermint oil + nigella sativa seed ext + hydrolyzed soy protein + green tea ext + yarrow ext + aloe vera ext + argan oil', 'Prime pharma', 'Lotion', 'لوشن', '', 'Hair care', '120 ml', 'Caffeine is indicated for the short term treatment of apnea of prematurity in infants and off label for the prevention and treatment of bronchopulmonary dysplasia caused by premature birth.[T716,L9851] In addition, it is indicated in combination with sodium benzoate to treat respiratory depression resulting from an overdose with CNS depressant drugs.[L9899] Caffeine has a broad range of over the counter uses, and is found in energy supplements, athletic enhancement products, pain relief products, as well as cosmetic products.[T716,L9854,L9872]', '', '', 621, '2025-07-31', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
